For any orders placed for delivery
outside of the UK
, your order is purchased from Global-e, our international fulfilment partner, and your contract is with them. Further information can be found in their
Privacy Policy
and
Terms of Service
.
When you pay for your order, your order information (including personal data) is transferred to the payment provider to facilitate the payment process. This is required to fulfil the contract and process your order. Your data will be processed and retained by the payment provider in accordance with their privacy policy, and might be transferred by them outside of the EEA. Depending on your location, we use the following payment providers:
Shopify Payments (
privacy policy
)
