                        consumer rights notice: California residents may reach the Compliant Assistance Unit of the
                        Division of Consumer Services for the California Department of Consumer Affairs by mail at 1625
                        North Market Blvd., Sacramento, CA 95834, or by telephone at (916) 445-1254 or (800) 952-5210.
